rComments: He is a good professor, really good at teaching, but maybe it's because of the nature of this course, there was literally no homework or practice except past exams in exam season. Therefore at the end your marks partially come down to talent rather than practice, which I personally believe to be unfair and tough.
teacherRatingTags: ['Gives good feedback', "Skip class? You won't pass.", 'Tough grader']

rComments: Great guy! Super funny and has a really chill personality. He marks pretty hard but is very fair. You will learn a lot about law with this guy. He tells great stories and is very open about his own career with the students. Great choice.

If you're doing 225 then you gotta take it with Professor Rybak! Such a cool guy; very chill and tried to make the class as interesting as possible especially with some of the dull concepts. Always looked forward to going to his class.

Great professor - very likeable, funny, caring guy and always there to help students, very good with responding to emails and provides detailed answers to questions. Lectures are interesting and helpful, especially since he makes them fun with his stories and way of teaching. No complaints whatsoever

Such a great prof!  By far the most likable prof at rotman.  He makes the boring material interesting with his hilarious lectures, very easy to listen to.  Responds very fast to email, and tells you exactly what you need to know for the exams.

One of the best professors at Rotman!! He is hilarious and very easy to talk to. Explains concepts very clearly and gives a lot of examples on how certain concepts work. Lectures are very interesting as he actually talks to the class and never just reads of the slides. Marks fairly but getting a high mark requires effort.

Rybak was a decent lecturer. He is funny, approachable, crystal clear, and helpful. However his class can get rather dry at times. If you ever have a question, just email him and he will respond so quickly! Text book was hard to understand, he even acknowledged this but he can't change it unfortunately. Overall fantastic teacher but mediocre class.
